Class RelatedMetadataElementSummary

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.RelatedMetadataElementSummary
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChildCategoryElement
public class RelatedMetadataElementSummary extends Object
RelatedBy contains the properties and header for a relationship retrieved from the metadata repository along with the stub of the related element.
